{"root":{"data":{"id":"di2c7je3vao0","created":1777130565863,"text":"游戏概念与机制设想"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c834w6bk0","created":1777130608842,"text":"连招体统","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c8i7cdi80","created":1777130641642,"text":"将连击的每段设置为不同层级,每段动作美感和复杂程度提升, 但是能在每个层级内挑选一个动作, 达到随机衔接招式的目的","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cbn6tj200","created":1777130887587,"text":"当敌人无法反抗, (比如眩晕)","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"fish-bone","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}